panels.description: Latest sequence number of a stream consumer.

targets.expr: sum(jetstream_consumer_delivered_consumer_seq{gke_cluster="$cluster", namespace=~"$namespace", app_kubernetes_io_instance=~"$server", stream_name=~"$stream", consumer_name=~"$consumer", is_consumer_leader="true"}) by (consumer_name)

panels.title: Total delivered messages

panels.description: Number of pending messages from a consumer (i.e. messages that are waiting to be sent to the consumer).

targets.expr: sum(jetstream_consumer_num_pending{gke_cluster="$cluster", namespace=~"$namespace", app_kubernetes_io_instance=~"$server", stream_name=~"$stream", consumer_name=~"$consumer", is_consumer_leader="true"}) by (consumer_name)

panels.title: Pending messages

panels.description: Number of pending acks from a consumer (i.e. messages that have been sent to the consumer but not acknowledged by the consumer yet).

targets.expr: sum(jetstream_consumer_num_ack_pending{gke_cluster="$cluster", namespace=~"$namespace", app_kubernetes_io_instance=~"$server", stream_name=~"$stream", consumer_name=~"$consumer", is_consumer_leader="true"}) by (consumer_name)

panels.title: Message Acks Pending

panels.description: Number of redelivered messages from a consumer.

panels.title: Consumer count
